      "language": "english",
      "review": "Terrible Wheel setup, switching to controller is even more dumb. They made LFB drop your rpms with throttle pinned. Car oversteers and sometimes just randomly steers itself without input. Using the clutch to correct oversteer is a joke, doesn't seem to do anything except make your rpms pinned and stay there. \n\nThe only thing good about this game is the idea of open world drifting. If they can make the cars fun to drive without losing your mind I'll pick it up again. Until then I'm going to save my money.",
