      "language": "english",
      "review": "this developers did a great job of combining both traffic and tracks so that you can experience both of them. As expected from the this developers previous games the handling is not that easy like carx u need to practice a bit and adapt to it but still its fun in its own way. i did try other features like customisation but livery and cockpit customs are unusable. there are different servers you will join as soon as u enter game that last for 2 hrs after that u will be kicked out. different missions to get money and points for upgrades, but the map is a little small... but considering its a early access game its a huge thumbs up as both keyboard and controller works just find i dont know about steering but im guessing it works. so at this point the major things that this game need is that customisation fixes and a lot of people",
