      "language": "english",
      "review": "So im 10 hours in - what do I think?\n\nWhile im no drifting expert, I've always loved to drift in Forza MS/Horizon, NFS games etc and have played a lot of Car X Drift Online.\n\nInitially when I started playing, I was considering getting a refund because I was spinning out on every corner with the starter car. Didnt matter how I tuned it, it always span out. Then I went and tried some other cars, put some upgrades into them and while I wasnt getting stupid angles, I was making points/money/etc to spend on further upgrades.\n\nWhile there isnt much \"to do\" in the game in terms of comps/events, I have been having a lot of fun just cruising from track to track, doing the odd car meet with other players and doing the odd bit of touge.\n\nLoads of cars but not a huge amount of customisation outside of changing your muffler and decals so would love to see further custom options.\n\nPersonally - worth the money IMO",
