        "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0,
        "playtime_at_review": 261,
        "last_played": 1702600099
      },
      "language": "english",
      "review": "As long as you are coming into this with the understanding that it is an early build and that it was made public relatively recently, it is a good thing to waste time on! Cars are incredibly nervous though, so I HIGHLY recommend softening up the suspension, loosening up the diff and so on. Good start thus far, will be interested to see where this goes!\n\nDon't expect it to be CarX though, you can feel the difference in physics, and there's not a lot of visual customization (though changing how the exhaust sounds when bouncing off the limiter is a neat touch!)",
